          "reviewBody": "This school needs to introspect and alter their approach to management. Had expected more from a brand like Bharti Vidyapeeth... Mismanagement of school uniforms, no canteen service, high attrition rate of good teachers, unclean toilets, no library or other co-cirricular activities for a long time. Mismanagement regarding days and very poor communication between parents and teachers viaa buggy app...These are some of the immediate concerns ..Not to mention the sky high tution and other fees ..Not recommended",
